{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "In the process of constructing UrbanKG, (Liu et al. 2023b) skillfully incorporated graph pooling technology into the system architecture to achieve deep integration and efficient processing of complex urban data.",
    "The system not only supports standard pooling operations such as summing, averaging, and maxima but also allows users to customize the pooling function according to specific needs, which greatly enhances the flexibility and adaptability of the system.",
    "Through subgraph extraction and aggregation, UrbanKG effectively reduces the complexity of data processing while retaining key information, providing a solid data foundation for intelligent urban decision-making.",
    "Aiming at the complexity of urban spatio-temporal mobility prediction, (Yang et al. 2024) designed a cross-modal graph pooling fusion neural network, which innovatively introduced a convolutional fusion mechanism to realize the joint optimization of the target and auxiliary graph embedding, to accurately extract and fuse the shared spatio-temporal mobility patterns.",
    "The differentiable pooling method that it adopted can effectively integrate the knowledge of the auxiliary system into the target system in a hierarchical structure, which significantly improves the accuracy and robustness of the prediction."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "In the process of constructing UrbanKG, (Liu et al. 2023b) skillfully incorporated graph pooling technology into the system architecture to achieve deep integration and efficient processing of complex urban data.",
    "Aiming at the complexity of urban spatio-temporal mobility prediction, (Yang et al. 2024) designed a cross-modal graph pooling fusion neural network, which innovatively introduced a convolutional fusion mechanism to realize the joint optimization of the target and auxiliary graph embedding, to accurately extract and fuse the shared spatio-temporal mobility patterns."
